OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cloudy day with outbreaks of
OL,6,Frain throughout. Rain will be
OL,7,Fespecially heavy and persistent in the
OL,8,Fmorning over Orkney and then Shetland
OL,9,Flater. Mostly light winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FMostly cloudy in the evening
OL,12,Fwith rain clearing to the north of
OL,13,FShetland and showers gradually easing
OL,14,Fover Orkney. Largely dry overnight
OL,15,Fwith just the odd light shower
OL,16,Fpossible.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
