OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FA mostly dry and cloudy day
OL,6,Fbut with some bright or sunny spells
OL,7,Fbreaking through. Outbreaks of rain
OL,8,Fspreading into Orkney in the evening.
OL,9,FLight southerly winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FCloudy
OL,12,Fwith outbreaks of rain on Tuesday.
OL,13,FBright spells and a few showers on
OL,14,FWednesday. Heavy rain spreads north
OL,15,Fearly Thursday to become largely dry
OL,16,Fand bright with strengthening winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
